            "title": "LHA Music Night！🎵",
            "summary": "On May 18th, 2022, we came together as a musical family at night to put on this amazing show. Thanks to all my classmates, Mr. Anthopoulos, and all the people who helped us behind the show during these six weeks of training. You have made&hellip;",
            "content_html": "\n  <p id=\"on-may-18th-2022-we-came-together-as-a-musical-family-at-night-to-put-on-this-amazing-show-thanks-to-all-my-classmates-mr-anthopoulos-and-all-the-people-who-helped-us-behind-the-show-during-these-six-weeks-of-training-you-have-made-me-truly-love-music-and-i-am-honored-to-be-a-part-of-this-band-it-will-always-be-a-good-part-of-my-memory\">\n    On May 18th, 2022, we came together as a musical family at night to put on this amazing show. Thanks to all my classmates, Mr. Anthopoulos, and all the people who helped us behind the show during these six weeks of training. You have made me truly love music and I am honored to be a part of this band. It will always be a good part of my memory.\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    Video:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/CduMSNkF_jQ/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/CduMSNkF_jQ/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link</a>\n  </p>\n\n  <div  class=\"gallery-wrapper gallery-wrapper--full\">\n    <div class=\"gallery\" data-columns=\"3\">\n      <figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/8/gallery/281329533_161480786333055_2061872505733550605_n-2.jpg\" data-size=\"1080x811\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/8/gallery/281329533_161480786333055_2061872505733550605_n-2-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"541\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" />\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/8/gallery/281337766_378658034190716_7606290427656722646_n-2.jpg\" data-size=\"1080x814\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/8/gallery/281337766_378658034190716_7606290427656722646_n-2-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"543\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" />\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/8/gallery/281440582_461400769086479_7925680810180482604_n-2.jpg\" data-size=\"1080x814\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/8/gallery/281440582_461400769086479_7925680810180482604_n-2-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"543\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" />\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure>\n    </div>\n  </div>",
