            "url": "https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/graduation-2022-of-lha/index.html",
            "title": "Graduation 2022 of LHA🎓",
            "summary": "Instagram In August 2022 I will graduate from LHA. Thanks to all the professors who help me a lot. (Help me get through the language barrier) I will continue my studying at CÉGEP. That's a new challenge for me. I will keep working hard🙃",
            "content_html": "<figure class=\"post__image\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lhaclassof2022/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Instagram</a><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lhaclassof2022/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-base); font-size: inherit; font-weight: var(--font-weight-normal); border-bottom: 3px solid rgba(var(--yellow), 1);\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  style=\"outline: 3px solid rgba(var(--primary-color-rgb), 0.55)  !important;\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e7/Instagram_logo_2016.svg/800px-Instagram_logo_2016.svg.png\" data-is-external-image=\"true\"  alt=\"\" width=\"29\" height=\"29\"></figure></a></p>\n<p>In August 2022 I will graduate from LHA. Thanks to all the professors who help me a lot. (Help me get through the language barrier) I will continue my studying at CÉGEP. That's a new challenge for me. I will keep working hard🙃</p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-columns=\"1\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/5/gallery/2021_11_26_19_56_IMG_6883.JPG\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/5/gallery/2021_11_26_19_56_IMG_6883-thumbnail.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/5/gallery/Wei-Biao-Ti-1-Kao-Bei.jpg\" data-size=\"2400x3360\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/5/gallery/Wei-Biao-Ti-1-Kao-Bei-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"1008\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>",
