            "summary": "In 2021-2022, I started to host a 3D printing club with Ms. Stark at LaurenHill Academy. The idea comes to my mind just because I want to pass on this technology and let more people enjoy it. I try my best to prepare for the&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"align-left\">In 2021-2022, I started to host a 3D printing club with Ms. Stark at LaurenHill Academy. The idea comes to my mind just because I want to pass on this technology and let more people enjoy it. I try my best to prepare for the courses. The results are very satisfying and I have made a lot of friends and gotten a lot of people to like 3-d print technology!</p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/4/gallery/20211123_160925.jpg\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/4/gallery/20211123_160925-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/4/gallery/20211124_110052.jpg\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/4/gallery/20211124_110052-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/4/gallery/20211124_115045-2.jpg\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://zangjiucheng.github.io/blog.page/media/posts/4/gallery/20211124_115045-2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>",
